def bubble_sort(arr):
    n = len(arr)
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(0, n-i-1):
            if arr[j] _____ arr[j+1]:
                arr[j], arr[j+1] = arr[j+1], arr[j]
```

Complete the binary search implementation:
```
def binary_search(arr, target):
    left, right = 0, len(arr) - 1
    while left <= right:
        mid = (left + right) // 2
        if arr[mid] == target:
            return mid
        elif arr[mid] < target:
            left = mid + 1
        else:
            right = mid _____ 1
    return -1
```

