Complete the code for two-pointer technique to find pair with given sum:
```
def find_pair(arr, target):
    arr.sort()
    left, right = 0, len(arr) - 1
    while left < right:
        current_sum = arr[left] + arr[right]
        if current_sum == target:
            return True
        elif current_sum < target:
            left += 1
        else:
            right _____ 1
    return False
```

